151
00:13:16,643 --> 00:13:19,063
ako aj jeho agenta ducha.

152
00:13:20,823 --> 00:13:24,822
Keď ovládneme celú NIS, drevené rezby...

153
00:13:24,823 --> 00:13:28,693
