- Otec.
- Do Ha.

204
00:17:17,263 --> 00:17:18,753
Vitaj späť.

205
00:17:19,763 --> 00:17:21,553
Vďaka.

206
00:17:23,273 --> 00:17:25,562
Vďakabohu, spravodlivosť vždy zvíťazí.

207
00:17:25,563 --> 00:17:26,843
Tí bastardi.

208
00:17:29,153 --> 00:17:30,433
